{"tid":1180581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"敢言杜汶澤搞團遊馬拉","createTime":"2019-06-01T02:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T06:56:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a30d6bbaaa2a6ba5a273e4b7189474517b902f2","tid":1180581,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190601/20692581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F20692581&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=797b70c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F20692581&h=dc3db7fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190601/20692581</a><br />\n<br />\n敢言杜汶澤搞團遊馬拉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190601/large/01ec1p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190601%2Flarge%2F01ec1p10.jpg&h=88c7673b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿澤主持的節目《走佬去馬拉》日前播出時大受歡迎。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被內地封殺的藝人不只黃耀明，還有一向敢言的杜汶澤，阿澤被內地封殺後轉戰東南亞市場，更在馬來西亞開設電影公司。識飲識食的阿澤早前為ViuTV主持旅遊節目《走佬去馬拉》大受歡迎，阿澤昨日在fb宣佈：「本人即將承辦馬拉豪食團，有興趣跟我去食好西嘅朋友，密切留意！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【走在最前】撐雨傘運動被內地封殺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190601/large/01ec1p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190601%2Flarge%2F01ec1p11.jpg&h=446d67a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿澤將帶團到馬來西亞食好西。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n阿澤昨日接受《蘋果》訪問，透露組美食團的原因：「因為自從《走佬去馬拉》播出後，好多人打嚟問我嗰度啲嘢食喺邊度，去到住邊度、邊度玩呀，我心諗不如直情搞團帶佢哋去玩啦。」阿澤透露目前正在籌備緊階段，團名將叫做「走佬去馬拉豪食團」：「去食一啲就算連當地人都好難搵到嘅嘢食，同埋畀我搵到個resort成萬呎，連埋後花園有兒童遊樂場，最啱一家大細去玩，會將啲好嘅嘢食運晒去間屋度，間屋又有廚師幫你整番佢。」問到同團如果有小朋友，可會留言言詞用語？阿澤笑謂：「有細路喺度，梗係唔講粗口，我哋呢啲做藝人任性，做生意會好理性。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：何永寧  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【網民同悼】「六四畫面記憶猶新」<br />\n<br />\n【走在最前】撐雨傘運動被內地封殺<br />\n【網民同悼】「六四畫面記憶猶新」<br />\n達明一派《回憶有罪》登iTunes榜首明哥念六四30「願廣場上聲音不會滅」"},{"pid":"8951898f2d196330cae55f4a5215328f037d25df","tid":1180581,"uid":25367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=9fc66b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a>"},{"pid":"775cc57b5af535e58c5fcbc7b5249291f5bec146","tid":1180581,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:01:18.000Z","msg":"應該六四都搞埋反送中啦<br />\n歷史事件係咁意算啦"},{"pid":"5820042dafd3fc0cb7825ef9dd37381030512f46","tid":1180581,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"有冇旅行社牌"}]}